- (LAUGHTER)

45:29.438 --> 45:30.506
Where were we?

45:30.573 --> 45:33.042
Uh... Latour, read.

45:33.743 --> 45:36.612
I do not read Latin.

45:36.679 --> 45:39.048
- You do not even read.
- (LAUGHTER)

45:39.114 --> 45:41.350
