45:59.401 --> 46:02.137
"A new love
expels an old one."

46:02.204 --> 46:04.206
(GUESTS EXCLAIM IN AWE)

46:06.208 --> 46:07.576
- Too true.
- (GUESTS CHUCKLE)

46:07.643 --> 46:11.313
Well, it appears we have a
squire with a hidden talent.

46:11.380 --> 46:12.615
Read, do read.

46:17.152 --> 46:18.420
Uh...

46:18.487 --> 46:20.623
(READING IN LATIN)

46:21.690 --> 46:23.325
(IN ENGLISH) The rule
of love number four.

46:23.392 --> 46:26.362
"Love is always growing,

46:27.196 --> 46:28.264
"or diminishing."

46:28.330 --> 46:30.232
- (ALL LAUGHING)
- Insolent bastard!

46:30.299 --> 46:33.602
(LAUGHING) He knows you.

46:33.669 --> 46:35.805
(JACQUES READING IN LATIN)

46:41.343 --> 46:46.081
(IN ENGLISH) "Nothing prevents a
woman from being loved by two men.

46:46.148 --> 46:48.417
(GUESTS EXCLAIM TEASINGLY)

46:51.520 --> 46:53.757
"Or a man from being
loved by two women."

46:53.823 --> 46:55.257
(LAUGHTER)

46:55.691 --> 46:57.293
(APPLAUSE)

46:57.660 --> 46:59.161
Well read.

47:01.697 --> 47:04.233
- (ALL EXCLAIM AND LAUGH)
- Oh. Come, come.

47:04.300 --> 47:06.602
If you run,
I will only chase you.

47:06.669 --> 47:09.104
(ALL CLAPPING RHYTHMICALLY)

47:13.342 --> 47:15.678
Wow, he grows serious.

47:15.745 --> 47:18.815
WOMAN 1: No! No! No!
(LAUGHING)

47:18.882 --> 47:20.349
No!

47:20.416 --> 47:22.184
(LAUGHING)

47:24.520 --> 47:27.623
- (ALL CHEERING)
- No! No! No!

47:29.558 --> 47:31.560
(WOMAN 1 STRUGGLING)

47:31.627 --> 47:34.096
(LAUGHING) No! No! No!

47:38.467 --> 47:40.202
(WOMEN LAUGHING)

47:40.269 --> 47:41.537
This customer is rough.

47:42.371 --> 47:43.505
WOMAN 1: No!

47:43.572 --> 47:44.774
- JACQUES: And strong.
- (MOANS)

47:46.843 --> 47:49.713
Here, come take
some evil inside you.

47:51.781 --> 47:52.849
(GRUNTS)

47:52.916 --> 47:54.249
- WOMAN 2: Pierre!
- Oh.

47:54.316 --> 47:55.351
Come, Pierre.

47:55.919 --> 47:57.186
PIERRE: Great!

47:57.252 --> 47:58.320
- Pierre.
- (PIERRE GRUNTS)

47:58.387 --> 47:59.588
